S.FORM: 請別說不amana sakamu tu kai' amana ka kai sa, mahida siwacaahay ku lahud, amica kapah tu sakaku,mahida mialaay tu tuud, sawni maala sawni malawpes, caay ka patay ku dimiad, amana pikai tunipiawda nu maku, amana' pikaisa a malalitemuh. nu maudipay, pinakiya haw ku saka lalitemuh, sakay udip, pina ku kapahay a cabay,alahican malalitemuh, lalitemuh saca, caay ka tadikud, pasayda han tu taayaw. .

請別說不amana sakamo to kai' amana ka kai sa, mahida siwacaahay ko lahod, amica kapah to sakako,mahida mialaay to tood, sawni maala sawni malawpes, caay ka patay ko dimiad, amana pikai tonipiawda no mako, amana' pikaisa a malalitemoh. no maodipay, pinakiya haw ko saka lalitemoh, sakay odip, pina ko kapahay a cabay,alahican malalitemoh, lalitemoh saca, caay ka tadikod, pasayda han to taayaw. .
